@startuml Stock_Adjustment_Sequence
autonumber

skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 10
skinparam defaultFontSize 20
skinparam maxMessageSize 400

actor "Admin Sistem" as Admin
boundary "UI Penyesuaian Stok" as UI
control "Stock Adjustment Controller" as Controller
database "Database" as DB

== 1. Skenario & Input ==
Admin -> UI : Buka menu produk & stok
alt Metode: Lembar Kerja
    Admin -> UI : Pilih & Cetak Dokumen Stok Opname
else Metode: Langsung (Real-time)
    note over UI : Menuju pencarian produk
end

Admin -> UI : Scan / Masukkan Nama Produk
UI -> Controller : Ambil data produk(id)
Controller -> DB : Query data stok & varian
DB --> UI : Data Produk Lengkap

Admin -> UI : Masukkan stok fisik aktual per varian
UI -> UI : Hitung total stok dasar & selisih (Client-side)

== 2. Konfirmasi & Eksekusi ==
Admin -> UI : Review selisih & Tekan tombol Konfirmasi
UI -> Controller : Simpan penyesuaian stok

activate Controller
Controller -> DB : Update stok produk
activate DB

Controller -> DB : Catat mutasi stok (adjustment)
DB --> Controller : Konfirmasi Simpan
deactivate DB

alt Proses Berhasil
    Controller --> UI : Konfirmasi Berhasil
    UI --> Admin : Notifikasi Berhasil & Update Tampilan
else Proses Gagal
    Controller --> UI : Notifikasi Gagal
    UI --> Admin : Notifikasi Gagal (Rollback transaksi)
end
deactivate Controller

@enduml